title: McCarter scores three ways, Saints march past Eagle's View
text:
McCarter scores three ways, Saints march past Eagle's View 
Sat, Oct 3, 2015 @ 12:16 am 
CEDAR CREEK 54 
EAGLE’S VIEW 12 
Tron McCarter scored rushing, receiving and defensive TDs and accounted for more than 300 all-purpose yards as the Saints defeated Eagle’s View (1-4, 0-1 District 2-2A). ... Ivory Durham also passed for three TDs for Cedar Creek (4-1, 1-0). ... Elijah Spivey added a 60-yard rushing TD and Shannon Mickens capped the scoring with two TDs for the Saints.
